OL,3,CSecond boy charged with the murder of
OL,4,C17-year-old Jamal Coombes in Battersea
OL,6,FA second boy has been charged with
OL,7,Fmurder over the death of a 17-year-old
OL,8,Fin south-west London.
OL,10,FThe 15-year-old, who has not been
OL,11,Fnamed because of his age, will appear
OL,12,Fat Ealing Magistrates' Court on
OL,13,FTuesday charged with murder and
OL,14,Fposession of a knife.
OL,16,FA second suspect, a boy aged 14, is
OL,17,Ffacing the same charges and is due to
OL,18,Fappear at the Old Bailey on Thursday.
