OL,3,CSecond boy charged with the murder of
OL,4,C17-year-old Jamal Coombes in Battersea
OL,6,FThey are both accused of murdering
OL,7,FJamal Coombes, 17, who died after a
OL,8,Fconfrontation in Glycena Road,
OL,9,FBattersea, at 4.20am on Saturday.
OL,11,FA boy and a girl, both aged 15, who
OL,12,Fwere arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,13,Fon Saturday have been released on bail
